msgstr ""
"Les types primitifs comme [`u8`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/std/primitive.u8.html)."

#: src/std-types/docs.md
msgid ""
"Standard library types like [`Option`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/std/option/enum."
