msgstr ""
"Les types de bibliothèque standard comme [`Option`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/std/"
"option/enum.Option.html) ou [`BinaryHeap`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/std/"
"collections/struct.BinaryHeap.html)."

#: src/std-types/docs.md
