#: src/welcome-day-3.md src/welcome-day-4-afternoon.md
msgid ""
"Including 10 minute breaks, this session should take about 2 hours and 20 minutes. It "
"contains:"
msgstr ""
"En comptant les pauses de 10 minutes, cette session devrait durer environ 2 heures et 20 "
