#: src/idiomatic/foundations-api-design/meaningful-doc-comments/library-vs-application-docs.md
msgid ""
"You might see elaborate documentation for fundamental APIs that repeats the names and "
"type signatures. Stable and highly reusable code can afford this with a positive RoI."
msgstr ""

#: src/idiomatic/foundations-api-design/meaningful-doc-comments/library-vs-application-docs.md
#, fuzzy
