"You can explore the [`Mutex` implementation in Rust’s std library](https://doc.rust-lang."
"org/std/sync/struct.Mutex.html) as an example of a production-ready mutex. The [`Mutex` "
"from the `parking_lot` crate](https://docs.rs/parking_lot/latest/parking_lot/type.Mutex."
