#: src/idiomatic/leveraging-the-type-system/extension-traits/should-i-define-an-extension-trait.md
msgid ""
"Extension methods can be easier to discover than free functions. Language servers (e.g., "
"`rust-analyzer`) will suggest them if you type `.` after an instance of the foreign type."
msgstr ""

#: src/idiomatic/leveraging-the-type-system/extension-traits/should-i-define-an-extension-trait.md
