"This example shows modelling gaining administrator privileges for a chat client with a "
"password and giving a user a moderator rank once those privileges are gained. The "
"`AdminToken` type acts as \"proof of correct user privileges.\""
msgstr ""

#: src/idiomatic/leveraging-the-type-system/token-types/permission-tokens.md
